sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Browser
    participant WebServer
    participant Cache
    participant Database
    
    User->>Browser: Click Login
    Browser->>WebServer: POST /login
    WebServer->>Cache: Check session
    WebServer->>Database: Query user
    Database-->>WebServer: User data
    WebServer-->>Browser: Set cookie
    Browser-->>User: Show dashboard
    
